# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __getitem__, __setitem__, __delitem__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All fifteen values are false; no pathlib class implements the subscript
# access, assignment, or deletion protocols in its own __dict__.
# Path objects are immutable filesystem path value types; the subscript
# protocol ([], []= , del []) is not part of the pathlib API.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

